com.unboundid.util.ssl.cert

Enum NamedCurve

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<NamedCurve>
      • com.unboundid.util.ssl.cert.NamedCurve
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<NamedCurve>

    @ThreadSafety(level=COMPLETELY_THREADSAFE)
public enum NamedCurve
extends java.lang.Enum<NamedCurve>
    This enum defines a set of OIDs that are known to be associated with elliptic curve keys.
